IT Acceptable Use Policy
 All employees must adhere to the following IT policies to maintain cybersecurity and productivity.
 VPN Access:- Use the company-provided VPN to access internal systems when working remotely.- Contact it-support@company.com for VPN setup.
 Device Usage:- Personal use of company devices should be minimal and comply with company policies.- Report any suspicious activity or phishing attempts immediately.
 Password Policy:- Passwords must be updated every 90 days.- Use a combination of uppercase, lowercase, numbers, and symbols.
